sourcesContent:
import React from 'react'
import {Box, Center, ChakraProvider, Divider, Text, Stack, Image, Container, ListItem, UnorderedList, Heading } from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Center>
                <Box w="1364px">
                    <Divider mt="100px" />
                </Box>
            </Center>
            <Container maxW="1364px">
                <Stack>
                    <Box mb={20}>
                        <Box>
                            <Heading ml="15px" mb="15px" as="h4" size="md">Learn</Heading>
                            <UnorderedList style={{listStyleType: "none"}}>
                                <ListItem>Help center</ListItem>
                                <ListItem>Join ZEN team</ListItem>
                                <ListItem>Privacy Policy</ListItem>
                                <ListItem>Cookies</ListItem>
                                <ListItem>Terms of use</ListItem>
                            </UnorderedList>
                        </Box>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mb={20}>
                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="360px">
                            <Box>
                                <Image src="/zen-zero-effort-grey.png" />
                                <Box maxW="800px" mt={5}>
                                    <Text fontSize="13px" color="#AAAAAA">ZEN.COM is a licensed financial institution under the supervision of the Central Bank of Lithuania approved by European Banking Authority for 31 countries. Registration number of the company 304749651, VAT ID LT100011714916. License of electronic money institutions number LB000457. Share capital 2.185.000,00 EUR. Company address: Mėsinių g. 5, LT-01133, Vilnius, Lithuania. Sales Office: ul. Emilii Plater 53, 00-113 Warsaw, Poland.</Text>
                                </Box>
                            </Box>
                            <Box>
                                <Image w="175px" src="/pci-certificate-logo.png" mt={10} />
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Footer
